{"tid":636310,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X獨佔手機市場利潤35%　等同600多間Android廠商總和5倍","createTime":"2018-04-20T17:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T04:11:45.000Z","uid":85180,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b28b546802f914550c5892a6772f46f22ca2f31c","tid":636310,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"iPhone X獨佔手機市場利潤35%　等同600多間Android廠商總和5倍<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道Apple iPhone的利潤較其他手機高出幾倍，而早幾年更有報告指出全球智能手機的利潤均集中在Apple iPhone手機當中，而根據Counterpoint 發表的最新報告顯示，Apple iPhone X佔據了整個手機市場利潤的35%，這是600多間Android廠商總和的5倍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=1489a6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（Mobile Magazine）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據市場調查公司Counterpoint所發表的報告指出，2017年度第四季度全球市場整體利潤同比下跌了1%，而iPhone X一款手機就佔了整個手機行業的利潤高達35%！<br />\n分析師Karn Chauhan在一份聲明提及，iPhone X只開售了2個多月，但已佔整個手機市場營收21%，而整體利潤的35%。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，以往舊iPhone沒有因為新型號的iPhone推出而令其過時，反而舊機款同樣為Apple貢獻利潤，當中包括iPhone 8/8Plus、iPhone 7/7 Plus、iPhone 6、iPhone 6S等。報告最後指出雖然iPhone X銷量沒有之前預期那麼高，但基於新舊手機的貢獻，令到Apple佔了2017年度第4季度智能手機86%的利潤。"},{"pid":"adf3822247476a4943376fe37acc758ab812161a","tid":636310,"uid":52023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:44:10.000Z","msg":"AAPL已"},{"pid":"10430ffef7734211e9139ba92cc575aaf3e2c6b6","tid":636310,"uid":66779,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T18:05:22.000Z","msg":"等睇ifan拎哩樣嘢嚟打飛機，睇吓邊個面對人哋喺自己身上賺得多哩件事都要J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5e89730d6a9a51a30253e4cad0b78723532d9f","tid":636310,"uid":38291,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"咁好賺，因為班傻迷支持，信仰充值<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc